Name: Total Students
Description: Count of unique students enrolled in the selected term(s).

Name: Total Credit Hours
Description: Sum of all credit hours enrolled.

Name: Female Students
Expression:
VAR FemaleIDs =
    CALCULATETABLE(
        VALUES(biograph_master[ID_NUM]),
        biograph_master[GENDER] = F"

Name: Male Students
Expression:
VAR MaleIDs =
    CALCULATETABLE(
        VALUES(biograph_master[ID_NUM]),
        biograph_master[GENDER] = M"

Name: First Gen Students
Expression:
VAR FirstGenIDs =
    CALCULATETABLE(
        VALUES(student_master[ID_NUM]),
        student_master[FIRST_GENERATION] IN {Y"

Name: Avg Term GPA
Description: Average GPA for the selected term.

Name: Persistence Rate
Description: Percentage of fall students returning in spring.
Expression:
VAR CurrentYr = SELECTEDVALUE(stud_term_sum_div[YR_CDE])
VAR FallStudents =
    CALCULATETABLE(
        VALUES(stud_term_sum_div[ID_NUM]),
        stud_term_sum_div[TRM_CDE] = 10"

Name: Graduated Students
Expression:
VAR StudentsInContext = VALUES(stud_term_sum_div[ID_NUM])
VAR GraduatedIDs =
    CALCULATETABLE(
        VALUES(degree_history[ID_NUM]),
        NOT(ISBLANK(degree_history[DTE_DEGR_CONFERRED])),
        ALL(degree_history)
    )
RETURN
CALCULATE(
    DISTINCTCOUNT(stud_term_sum_div[ID_NUM]),
    stud_term_sum_div[ID_NUM] IN GraduatedIDs,
    stud_term_sum_div[ID_NUM] IN StudentsInContext
)

Name: YoY Student Change
Description: Year-over-year percentage change in student enrollment
Expression:
VAR CurrentYearText = MAX(stud_term_sum_div[YR_CDE])
  VAR IsNumeric = NOT(ISERROR(VALUE(CurrentYearText)))
  VAR CurrentYear = IF(IsNumeric, VALUE(CurrentYearText), BLANK())
  VAR PriorYearText = IF(IsNumeric, FORMAT(CurrentYear - 1, 0")

Name: YoY Indicator
Description: Arrow indicator showing year-over-year change direction
Expression:
VAR Change = [YoY Student Change]
RETURN
    SWITCH(
        TRUE(),
        Change > 0, ▲ " & FORMAT(Change

Name: New Students
Description: Count of students in their first term at the institution
Expression:
VAR CurrentYear = MAX(stud_term_sum_div[YR_CDE])
  VAR CurrentTerm = MAX(stud_term_sum_div[TRM_CDE])
  RETURN
  CALCULATE(
      DISTINCTCOUNT(stud_term_sum_div[ID_NUM]),
      FILTER(
          VALUES(stud_term_sum_div[ID_NUM]),
          VAR StudentID = stud_term_sum_div[ID_NUM]
          VAR FirstYear =
              CALCULATE(
                  MIN(stud_term_sum_div[YR_CDE]),
                  ALL(stud_term_sum_div),
                  stud_term_sum_div[ID_NUM] = StudentID
              )
          VAR FirstTerm =
              CALCULATE(
                  MIN(stud_term_sum_div[TRM_CDE]),
                  ALL(stud_term_sum_div),
                  stud_term_sum_div[ID_NUM] = StudentID,
                  stud_term_sum_div[YR_CDE] = FirstYear
              )
          RETURN FirstYear = CurrentYear && FirstTerm = CurrentTerm
      )
  )

Name: Avg Course Load
Description: Average number of courses per student

Name: High GPA Students
Description: Count of students with term GPA >= 3.5 (Dean's List potential)

Name: High GPA Percentage
Description: Percentage of students with high GPA

Name: Probation Students
Description: Count of students on academic probation (GPA < 2.0)

Name: Probation Percentage
Description: Percentage of students on academic probation

Name: Enrollment Trend
Description: Enrollment count for trend line charts

Name: Credit Hours Trend
Description: Credit hours for trend line charts

Name: Prior Year Students
Description: Student count for same term in prior year
Expression:
VAR CurrentYearText = SELECTEDVALUE(stud_term_sum_div[YR_CDE])
  VAR CurrentTerm = SELECTEDVALUE(stud_term_sum_div[TRM_CDE])
  VAR IsNumeric = NOT(ISERROR(VALUE(CurrentYearText)))
  VAR PriorYearText = IF(IsNumeric, FORMAT(VALUE(CurrentYearText) - 1, 0")

Name: GPA Color
Description: Hex color code based on GPA for conditional formatting
Expression:
VAR AvgGPA = [Avg Term GPA]
RETURN
    SWITCH(
        TRUE(),
        AvgGPA >= 3.5, #2E7D32"

Name: Enrollment Change Color
Description: Hex color code based on enrollment change for conditional formatting
Expression:
VAR Change = [YoY Student Change]
RETURN
    SWITCH(
        TRUE(),
        Change > 0.05, #2E7D32"

Name: Selected Term
Description: Displays the currently selected term and year

Name: Students by Ethnicity
Description: Count of students by selected ethnicity (handles multi-racial)
Expression:
VAR EthnicityStudents =
    CALCULATETABLE(
        VALUES(ethnic_race_report[ID_NUM]),
        ethnic_race_report
    )
RETURN
    CALCULATE(
        DISTINCTCOUNT(stud_term_sum_div[ID_NUM]),
        TREATAS(EthnicityStudents, stud_term_sum_div[ID_NUM])
    )

Name: Ethnicity Percentage
Description: Percentage of students by selected ethnicity

Name: Fall-to-Fall Retention Count
Expression:
VAR CohortYr = SELECTEDVALUE(CohortYears[CohortYear])
  VAR NextYr = SELECTEDVALUE(CohortYears[NextYear])

  VAR FallStudentsStart =
      CALCULATETABLE(
          VALUES(stud_term_sum_div[ID_NUM]),
          stud_term_sum_div[YR_CDE] = CohortYr,
          stud_term_sum_div[TRM_CDE] = 10"
